                     <hi rend="largeCaps">WILLIAM ROPER</hi> (18)</persName>
                  <rs id="t18671028-969-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18671028-969-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="deception"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18671028-969-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="forgery"></interp>, Felo<lb></lb>niously forging and uttering an older for the payment of 3<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 15<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., with intent to defraud. Rowley having been before convicted, to which </rs>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">ROWLEY</hi>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">

                     <rs id="t18671028-969-verdict-1" type="verdictDescription">
                        <interp inst="t18671028-969-verdict-1" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18671028-969-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="pleadedGuilty"></interp>PLEADED GUILTY.</rs>
                  </hi>—<hi rend="italic">
                     <rs id="t18671028-969-punishment-39" type="punishmentDescription">
                        <interp inst="t18671028-969-punishment-39" type="punishmentCategory" value="imprison"></interp>
